{"tid":2027490,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"國安法鋒霸，違約金高達4000M！","createTime":"2020-05-21T11:52:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T12:23:35.000Z","uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"12a20f8b7843221a00e7f04ee84a049cb65fdbab","tid":2027490,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T11:52:40.000Z","msg":"上周末的联赛中，北京国安再次遭到一场失利，半个月内从领头羊位置跌落，已经距离榜首的广州恒大4分，争冠处于劣势。在比埃拉受伤后，球队的进攻也出现了大问题，而巴坎布从非洲杯回来后一直&ldquo;快乐&rdquo;，让人逐渐无法容忍。据《足球报》记者白国华爆料，国安已经正式向塞维利亚前锋本耶德尔报价。<br />\n<br />\n白国华在微博中写道：&ldquo;本报，也就是足球报今日报道，国安开始正式报价本耶德尔。离注册截止日期还有两天时间，是不是他，很快就水落石出了。为了避免被人说带节奏和瞎猜，等夏窗关闭后，到时候再说说我了解到的国安引援情况吧。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MZuOgr3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMZuOgr3.jpg&h=8f5dd92c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"85a5236bbc12cbedef4d60615c3c4f94d0dfa8bd","tid":2027490,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T11:53:15.000Z","msg":"牛逼！"},{"pid":"59ff10e49bb44fc611dcab96091f817854bb69cd","tid":2027490,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T11:53:35.000Z","msg":"本耶德尔今年28岁，是一名法国国脚，共代表法国队出战了4次。上赛季，本耶德尔代表塞维利亚出战54次，打入30球助攻11次，非常高效。之前有传闻，本耶德尔由于希望参加明年的欧洲杯，因此希望留在五大联赛效力，但是一旦北京国安送出高昂报价，不排除他登陆中超的可能。<br />\n不过北京国安想要拿下本耶德尔并不容易，他的违约金高达4000万欧元，加上调节费，可能需要花费8000万欧元，这是北京国安需要考虑的。"},{"pid":"a99b3707b44d414850e22896f9f629743ff02737","tid":2027490,"uid":134997,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T11:53:56.000Z","msg":"兄弟是4000W吧 香港人才用M叫做万的 你造反了吗？"},{"pid":"f5433093aa04bb6a2a5cd87b2f82c572e6935e80","tid":2027490,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T11:53:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vwjFR0W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvwjFR0W.jpg&h=b03f0d4a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fbd2ed9d5025b6451eb51fe3407bc3c396da90cf","tid":2027490,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T11:54:35.000Z","msg":"國安法殺到<br />\nBen Yedder算唔算千古罪人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f14b52651843d198c4ff9d5fcb4cb98d7cb968ca","tid":2027490,"uid":243527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T11:54:52.000Z","msg":"我覺得今日都死道臨頭啦我要講啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2027426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2027426</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9a1410e4e878dee2b33db64f7604ed5be85aa466","tid":2027490,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T11:55:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8gLBp9Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8gLBp9Z.jpg&h=b5c1741c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"69e39e939a717e2f77f11133212d5939c4fd9766","tid":2027490,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85a5236bbc12cbedef4d60615c3c4f94d0dfa8bd","tid":2027490,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T11:53:15.000Z","msg":"牛逼！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T11:59:09.000Z","msg":"香港人堅持參與六四春晚30年<br />\n估唔到就咁比個法國佬玩死😪"},{"pid":"fe83e358198cc863d404bee803dde682b54aceba","tid":2027490,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T12:23:35.000Z","msg":"66666666666666666"}]}